PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FThe Defence Secretary John Healey
OL,8,Fannounced the UK had monitored covert
OL,9,FRussian submarines researching
OL,10,Fundersea infrastructure cables for
OL,11,Fmore than a month
OL,13,FThe UK and allies tracked a Russian
OL,14,Fattack submarine and two spy
OL,15,Fsubmarines in the North Atlantic for a
OL,16,Fmonth before they retreated, the
OL,17,FDefence Secretary John Healey has
OL,18,Frevealed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FHealey told reporters on Thursday that
OL,8,Fin the past few weeks, while many eyes
OL,9,Fwere trained on the Middle East
OL,10,Fcrisis, the UK - in partnership with
OL,11,FNorway and other allies - responded to
OL,12,F"increased Russian activity" in the
OL,13,FAtlantic Ocean.
OL,15,FThis involved a Russian Akula-class
OL,16,Fnuclear-powered attack submarine and
OL,17,Ftwo specialist submarines from
OL,18,FRussia's Ministry of Defence deep-sea
OL,19,Fresearch programme known as Gugi (Main
OL,20,FDirectorate of Deep-Sea Research), he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FOn the risk Russia posed to the UK,
OL,8,FHealey described Vladimir Putin as
OL,9,F"the primary threat to UK security".
OL,11,FAddressing him directly, Healey said:
OL,12,F"We see your activity over our cables
OL,13,Fand our pipelines, and you should know
OL,14,Fthat any attempt to damage them will
OL,15,Fnot be tolerated and will have serious
OL,16,Fconsequences."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FHealey said: "In response to the
OL,8,FRussian submarines, I can confirm that
OL,9,FI deployed our armed forces to track
OL,10,Fand to deter any malign activity by
OL,11,Fthese vessels.
OL,13,F"A Royal Navy warship and Royal Air
OL,14,FForce P8 aircraft alongside allies
OL,15,Fensured that the Russian submarines
OL,16,Fwere monitored 24/7.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,F"The Akula submarine subsequently
OL,8,Fretreated home, having been closely
OL,9,Ftracked throughout, and we continued
OL,10,Fto monitor the two Gugi submarines in
OL,11,Fand around wider UK waters.
OL,13,F"Our armed forces left them in no
OL,14,Fdoubt that they were being monitored,
OL,15,Fthat their movements were not covert,
OL,16,Fas President Putin planned, and that
OL,17,Ftheir attempted secret operation had
OL,18,Fbeen exposed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,F"Those Gugi submarines have now left
OL,8,FUK waters and headed back north," he
OL,9,Fadded, announcing the month-long
OL,10,Foperation had now concluded.
OL,12,FAsked what option remained open to the
OL,13,FUK to exact the "consequences" he
OL,14,Fmentioned should Russia damage vital
OL,15,Fundersea cables, Healey refused to
OL,16,Felaborate, saying only to do so would
OL,17,Fmake Russia "wiser".
OL,26,@pD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FHe did add that "because we were
OL,8,Fwatching them, we wanted to ensure
OL,9,Fthat we could warn them that their
OL,10,Fcovert operation had been exposed and
OL,11,Freduce the risk that they may attempt
OL,12,Fany action that could damage our
OL,13,Fpipelines or our cables."
OL,15,F"And I'm confident, we have no
OL,16,Fevidence that there has been any
OL,17,Fdamage, but with allies, we're sure
OL,18,Fthat this is now verifiable."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FMPs and peers have in the past warned
OL,8,Fthey are "not confident" the UK could
OL,9,Fprotect its undersea cables from
OL,10,Fattacks that could cause "catastrophic
OL,11,Fdisruption" to crucial financial and
OL,12,Fcommunications systems.
OL,14,FThe National Security Strategy
OL,15,FCommittee previously said UK offshore
OL,16,Fcables are "sufficiently vulnerable to
OL,17,Fmake them a target" for Putin if he
OL,18,Framps up his tests of Nato's
OL,19,Fresilience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FConcerns have been growing for some
OL,8,Ftime about the threat from foreign
OL,9,Frivals to undersea infrastructure that
OL,10,Fis crucial to internet connectivity.
OL,12,FThere is evidence that Moscow is
OL,13,Fpreparing for sabotage, with the same
OL,14,FRussian spy vessel Yantar caught
OL,15,Floitering over UK offshore cables in
OL,16,FJanuary.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FThe defence secretary was also asked
OL,8,Fwhether he was confident the UK had
OL,9,Fenough resources to appropriately
OL,10,Frespond to the increased global strain
OL,11,Fon defence.
OL,13,FHealey claimed Labour was spending
OL,14,F"more on defence now than ever
OL,15,Fbefore", but added, "in the face of
OL,16,Frising demands on defence, the prime
OL,17,Fminister said we must do more, spend
OL,18,Fmore, more quickly."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769064
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FThe question of defence spending comes
OL,8,Fat a time when Labour has faced
OL,9,Fcriticism for the delayed publication
OL,10,Fof the Defence Investment Plans,
OL,11,Fsetting out the next ten years of
OL,12,Fspending and strategy for the armed
OL,13,Fforces.
OL,15,FThe plan was originally promised for
OL,16,Fautumn 2025, and despite the prime
OL,17,Fminister saying two weeks ago it was
OL,18,Fon his desk, some reports have
OL,19,Fsuggested a dispute between the
OL,20,FMinistry of Defence and the Treasury
OL,21,Fover its cost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775769065
OL,3,CUK exposed covert Russian sub
OL,4,Coperation in North Atlantic, Healey
OL,5,Creveals
OL,7,FHealey himself has denied this is the
OL,8,Freason for the delay, but its absence
OL,9,Fhas led Tory leader Kemi Badenoch to
OL,10,Faccuse the PM of being "all mouth, no
OL,11,Ftrousers when it comes to defence".
OL,13,FBadenoch has called for the plan to be
OL,14,Fpublished when Parliament returns from
OL,15,Frecess next week.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
